content.rendered:
The Rally Square Ottoman matches our Rally Side Chairs & Rally Bar Stools, along with pairing well with any of our seating ranges.

Also often paired with our sofas for a warm, cosy feel in your restaurant, café, pub or bar.

1 year warranty.
